# 🌐 Portfolio – Melissa Largilliere

Welcome to my **personal portfolio**!  
This website showcases my background, projects, and skills in web development.  
It was built using **HTML** and **CSS**.

---

## 🧑‍💻 About Me

Hi! I’m **Melissa Largilliere**, a student developer at **Ada Tech School**.  
I’m passionate about creating user-friendly and meaningful projects.

In this portfolio, you’ll find projects I’ve completed during my studies as well as some I continue to improve.

---

## 🧱 Project Structure

### Main Files:

- **`index.html`** → Defines the website structure and content (About, Projects, Contact).
- **`style.css`** → Handles layout and design for the portfolio.

### Folder Structure:

```
.
├── index.html
├── style.css
├── images/
│   ├── Melissa.png
│   ├── background.svg
│   ├── bjrJS.jpg
│   ├── guess_a_number.png
│   ├── html_css_av_ex1.png
│   ├── html_css_av_ex3.png
│   └── copyright-svgrepo-com.svg
├── exercices/
│   ├── 01_bonjour_javascript.md/
│   ├── 02_guess_a_number.md/
│   ├── Exercice-1/
│   └── Exercice-3/
└── script.js
```

