## 💡 Features

- **About Me Section** — short introduction and portrait.
- **Projects Section** —
  - Visual preview of each project.
  - Direct links to live demos and GitHub repositories.
- **Footer** — includes links to:
  - [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/in/melissa-largilliere/)
  - [GitHub](https://github.com/piouoiq)
  - Email for direct contact.

---

## 🎨 Design

The portfolio follows a **clean and modern aesthetic**, featuring:

- Warm accent color (#EE8F15) for key elements.
- **Grid** and **Flexbox** layout for well-balanced content.
- **Hover animations** for links and images.
- Elegant **Google Fonts** (Gruppo, Josefin Sans, Montserrat, Manrope).

